    "causal_summary": "Phase 004 maintenance scenarios must be executed from scratch. All prior results are invalidated. The seven maintenance scenarios (EX-014, EX-035, EX-041, EX-042, EX-043, EX-044, EX-045) require fresh manual execution to verify that memory_index_scan, startup runtime compatibility guards, memory_update, memory_delete, bulk delete, health check diagnostics, and index scan and repair behave as specified by the canonical playbook. The five new scenarios (EX-041 through EX-045) expand coverage to state-mutating maintenance operations and diagnostic repair workflows.",
